00:50:26.620 --> 00:50:28.150
And so it's been five years.

00:50:28.150 --> 00:50:32.290
And everything had come to pass.

00:50:32.290 --> 00:50:35.880
And I was sort of doing this
reflection of, like, OK.

00:50:35.880 --> 00:50:37.720
I need to do my next five years.

00:50:37.720 --> 00:50:40.350
And now I'm scared shitless.

00:50:40.350 --> 00:50:43.650
This came to pass
and what do I do now?

00:50:43.650 --> 00:50:46.110
Like, the pressure
and the-- seeing

00:50:46.110 --> 00:50:48.850
the power of these
techniques sort of

00:50:48.850 --> 00:50:54.040
puts me in this place where
I'm at an impasse of how

00:50:54.040 --> 00:50:59.250
do I actually
visualize the next set?

00:50:59.250 --> 00:51:00.880
And I was just
wondering-- I don't know

00:51:00.880 --> 00:51:02.130
that I have a direct question.

00:51:02.130 --> 00:51:03.030
But I was just--

00:51:03.030 --> 00:51:04.220
DR. JAMES R. DOTY: No, I
understand what you're saying.

00:51:04.220 --> 00:51:05.690
Because sometimes
it can be scary,

00:51:05.690 --> 00:51:08.600
because you see
these events unfold

00:51:08.600 --> 00:51:11.090
before you, which
actually sometimes

00:51:11.090 --> 00:51:12.650
seem extraordinarily amazing.

00:51:12.650 --> 00:51:15.920
And I can say that with my own
experience as you read about.

00:51:15.920 --> 00:51:19.520
But the challenge
for I think all of us

00:51:19.520 --> 00:51:24.350
is we create these types
of narratives in our head,

00:51:24.350 --> 00:51:27.210
but we become attached to them.

00:51:27.210 --> 00:51:29.290
And then we start grasping.

00:51:29.290 --> 00:51:31.400
And this is the
biggest challenge--

00:51:31.400 --> 00:51:34.870
is because while we may
with good intention--

00:51:34.870 --> 00:51:37.770
with clarity of intention--
desire something, when

00:51:37.770 --> 00:51:42.250
we attach to it very strongly,
actually that interferes

00:51:42.250 --> 00:51:45.030
many times with it
actually manifesting.

00:51:45.030 --> 00:51:47.790
And when it doesn't
manifest, because you're

00:51:47.790 --> 00:51:51.690
so emotionally attached to it,
it has very negative effect.

00:51:51.690 --> 00:51:56.010
As an example, I've been working
on a project for some time.

00:51:56.010 --> 00:51:58.850
And it has done very well.

00:51:58.850 --> 00:52:00.820
And I had manifested
that it was going

00:52:00.820 --> 00:52:03.740
to go on in a different way.

00:52:03.740 --> 00:52:06.410
And it appears as though
that's not the case.

00:52:06.410 --> 00:52:07.940
And you know, my
initial response--

00:52:07.940 --> 00:52:13.830
because it was so important to
me-- is to bemoan the-- oh god.

00:52:13.830 --> 00:52:14.930
What did I do?

00:52:14.930 --> 00:52:16.520
What's wrong with me?

00:52:16.520 --> 00:52:20.680
And the thing, though, is that
by not having an attachment

00:52:20.680 --> 00:52:24.300
to that and still being
joyous and thankful

00:52:24.300 --> 00:52:28.080
of what you already have,
then you're liberated.

00:52:28.080 --> 00:52:32.330
Because what you're describing
is a fear of success.

00:52:32.330 --> 00:52:35.510
But why would you have
a fear of success?

00:52:35.510 --> 00:52:38.310
So you have to
remember that you can

00:52:38.310 --> 00:52:40.020
be joyous in every situation.

00:52:40.020 --> 00:52:41.800
And it's getting
back to it's not

00:52:41.800 --> 00:52:47.050
the situation-- it's how you
respond to the situation.

00:52:47.050 --> 00:52:48.797
And that's always,
always the case.

00:52:48.797 --> 00:52:50.630
And that's one of the
greatest gifts you can

00:52:50.630 --> 00:52:54.090
have-- is to see this reality.

00:52:54.090 --> 00:52:57.700
Because events have no power.

00:52:57.700 --> 00:53:00.010
It's you only give them power.

